        "setup": "From your server, call Atomic's `POST /access-token` endpoint using your [API key and secret](https://console.atomicfi.com/settings/credentials). The response contains a `publicToken`, which you then pass to client-side Transact SDK initialization or use in end-user-scoped API requests as `x-public-token`. Docs state this token defaults to a 24 hour expiry and can be set from 30 minutes to 30 days.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
      }
